                "invention-title": [
                    "Coal-fired boiler low-nitrogen combustion method and system coupled with plastic pyrolysis",
                    "一种耦合塑料热解的燃煤锅炉低氮燃烧的方法及系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a coal-fired boiler low-nitrogen combustion method and system coupled with plastic pyrolysis. The system comprises a waste plastic treatment device, a plastic pyrolysis device, a coal-fired boiler hearth, a pyrolysis gas purging device, a DSC system and an intelligent control system. The method comprises the following steps: S1, putting waste plastics into a crushing device, and treating to obtain plastic powder; s2, the plastic powder enters a plastic pyrolysis device, the plastic powder is pyrolyzed, and high-value plastic pyrolysis gas is obtained; and S3, the plastic pyrolysis volatile components are introduced into a burn-out area of the coal-fired boiler through a purging device, and the plastic pyrolysis volatile components and nitric oxide generated during pulverized coal combustion are mixed at the high temperature and react. High-value plastic pyrolysis gas rich in carbon monoxide, hydrogen, methane and the like is obtained by pyrolyzing the waste plastics, and the pyrolysis gas is introduced into the burnout area of the hearth of the coal-fired boiler so as to reduce the content of nitric oxide during combustion of pulverized coal and realize low-nitrogen combustion of the coal-fired boiler."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种耦合塑料热解的燃煤锅炉低氮燃烧的方法及系统。该系统包括废塑料处理装置、塑料热解装置、燃煤锅炉炉膛、热解气吹扫装置、DSC系统和智能控制系统；该方法包括步骤：S1.将废塑料投入粉碎装置中，处理后得到塑料粉末；S2.塑料粉末进入塑料热解装置中，使塑料粉末热解，得到高值塑料热解气；S3.通过吹扫装置将塑料热解挥发分通入燃煤锅炉燃尽区中，与煤粉燃烧时产生的氮氧化物在高温下混合并发生反应。本发明通过热解废塑料，得到富含一氧化碳、氢气和甲烷等气体的高值塑料热解气，并将热解气通入燃煤锅炉炉膛的燃尽区中，以减轻煤粉燃烧时氮氧化物的含量，实现燃煤锅炉低氮燃烧。"
                }
            ]
